Writers know this. Staring at a blank page with no question to answer is fe=
lt proof of Sartre=E2=80=99s observation: =E2=80=9CHumans are condemned to =
be free.=E2=80=9D (Maybe it had to be a writer who made that observation.) =
Fire up a blank page with a question in mind, however, and the world become=
