nifest Destiny</a><span> </span></em><span>&#8211; and I&#8217;ve read some=
 books on writing by the greats in the particular literary nonfiction form =
in which I want to write: John McPhee&#8217;s </span><em><a href=3D"https:/=
/substack.com/redirect/3e116291-3a5b-4174-b805-0bb1ed44565b?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXA=
wZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel=3D"" style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(54,55,55);text-decoration: underline;">Draft No. 4</a></em><span> an=
d Robert Caro&#8217;s </span><em><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/d=
