call the person who knew the person who knew the person, in case they might=
 have a nugget. We say curiosity is one of the most important traits in a p=
erson; </span><strong>questions are curiosity made tangible</strong><span>.=
</span></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height:=
 26px;font-size: 16px;"><span>We haven&#8217;t really talked about </span><=
