eight: 26px;font-size: 16px;">Pinning down your question isn&#8217;t easy &=
#8211; I&#8217;m still wrestling with mine &#8211; but it&#8217;s worth eve=
ry second you can give to it. It will shape everything else you do.</p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size=
: 16px;">Take some time this weekend &#8211; better yet, play hooky, take a=
 snow day or a sick day &#8211; and just think about the question you&#8217=
;d be happy spending a decade or six trying to answer. It&#8217;ll light up=
 your world more than any answer could.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;c=
olor: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">Long questions, sho=
rt answers.</p><div style=3D"font-size: 16px;line-height: 26px;"><hr style=
